CODE:
n=int(input("Enter no.of elements:"))
list1=[]
for i in range(0,n):
    e=int(input("enter list element:"))
    list1.append(e)
print("list=",list1)
print("Sum of elements in a list",sum(list1))
list1.reverse()
print("Reversed list is,\n",list1) 

OUTPUT:
Enter no.of elements:5
enter list element:2
enter list element:3
enter list element:9
enter list element:1
enter list element:4
list= [2, 3, 9, 1, 4]
Sum of elements in a list 19
Reversed list is,
 [4, 1, 9, 3, 2]
